  "original_title": "\u0dad\u0dca\u200d\u0dbb\u0dd2\u0dc0\u0dd3\u0dbd\u0dca \u0d9c\u0dcf\u0dc3\u0dca\u0dad\u0dd4\u0dad\u0dca \u0d89\u0dc4\u0dc5\u0da7",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Three wheeler fares also increased",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The President of the All Ceylon Three Wheelers' Union Lalith Dharmasekera told 'Lankadeepa' that the charge for the second kilometer has been increased by 10 rupees from 80 rupees to 90 rupees due to the increase in petrol prices.",
        "Mr. Dharmasekera further stated that the fare of Rs. 100 charged for the first kilometer has not been increased and that the authorities should intervene immediately to fix a permanent fare for three wheelers."
      ],
